sentences.sentence: Its female flowers are on the tip of currene growth, solitary or 2~3 (sometimes more) fascicled.
sentences.translation: 雌花生于当年生新梢顶端，单生或2～3朵簇生，有时更多。

sentences.sentence: Leaves variable, those on previous year's branches usually alternate, those on short branches approximate and often fascicled ;
sentences.translation: 易变的叶，那些在通常互生的第二年分枝上，那些在短枝紧靠和通常簇生上；
